It would look something like this:
```
service1.get(&quot;123&quot;).pipe(
    switchMap(() =&gt; combineLatest(service2.getAll(), service3.getAll())),
).subscribe(([service2Data, servoce3Data]) =&gt; {
    // do your stuff
});
```

